mples of decelerating and oscillatory boundary motion\nare worked out and illustrated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Dec 2016 19:53:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 3 Feb 2017 05:09:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-07-18"}
