approximately 1.7 dex in the case of G~29-38. Our\nnumerical simulations show that fingering convection is an efficient mechanism\nto mix the accreted material and that it must be taken into account in the\ndetermination of accretion rates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 29 Dec 2016 21:38:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-26"}
